An "abbreviated version" of the if statement

somecondition ? value1 : value2 ;

true ? : value1 : value2 : ==== > value1 will be printed
false ? : value1 : value2 : ==== > value2 will be printed
----------------------------------------
to simplify if statement , ternary operators are used : 
with if statement it will look like : 
let greeting;
if( isbeforenoon) {
greeting = "good morning"; }
else {
greeting = "good afternoon"; }

with ternary operator , it will look like :
let greeting = isbeforenoon ? : "good morning" : "good afternoon" ;

----------------------------------------------------------------------
nested ternary operator : 

let greeting = isbeforenoon ? "good morning " : isbeforefiveoclock ? : "good afternoon" : "good evening " ;
